org.odpi.openmetadata.commonservices.multitenant.OMVSServiceInstanceHandler
org.odpi.openmetadata.viewservices.myprofile.server.MyProfileInstanceHandler
public class MyProfileInstanceHandler extends OMVSServiceInstanceHandler
MyProfileInstanceHandler retrieves information from the instance map for the view service instances. The instance map is thread-safe. Instances are added and removed by the MyProfileAdmin class.
